From: Avery Felts <averyfelts@Averys-MacBook-Air.local>
Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 16:13:54 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 1/1] wow64: canonicalize Darwin ARM64 GUI pointers

---
 dlls/ntdll/unix/env.c            | 12 ++++
 dlls/ntdll/unix/signal_arm64.c   | 43 ++++++++++++--
 dlls/win32u/gdiobj.c             | 32 ++++++++++-
 dlls/winemac.drv/macdrv_main.c   |  2 +-
 dlls/winemac.drv/unixlib.h       | 24 ++++++++
 dlls/winspool.drv/cups.c         | 32 ++++++++---
 dlls/wow64win/user.c             | 98 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 dlls/wow64win/wow64win_private.h | 27 +++++++++
